fields.question: How do I rent a power bank?
fields.answer: Simply scan the QR code on any station, select your rental package, and make payment. The power bank will be dispensed automatically.

fields.question: What happens if I don't return the power bank on time?
fields.answer: Late fees will be charged according to our pricing policy. After 24 hours, the power bank will be considered lost and full replacement cost will be charged.
